  "actor_description": "The heat drains out and leaves something cleaner behind it. I get very still. My thoughts line up like tools on a table—what matters, what doesn’t, what I’ll do and when. My jaw locks, my voice wants to go flat. I’m not here to explode. I’m here to choose the moment.",
